HEADWORD: Generification
<hw>Ge*ner`i*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>genus</ets> kind, class + <ets>-ficare</ets> (in comp.) to make.
See <er>-fy</er>.]</ety> <def>The act or process of
generalizing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

